snippet.title: Battlefield 5 Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Never be the same. Join us for the Battlefield V Live Reveal on May 23 at 1 p.m. PT / 4 p.m. ET / 10 p.m. CEST, presented by The Daily Show host Trevor Noah and the DICE development team. Don’t miss out – set a calendar reminder for the event: http://x.ea.com/46500

Subscribe and be the first to see the full Battlefield V reveal trailer and other upcoming videos: http://bit.ly/270eMcA
